">8. Tiếp tuc trong package com.laptrinhjavaweb.api tạo 1 file java Application.java v&agrave; copy đoạn code b&ecirc;n dưới v&agrave;o file</span></span></p>\n\n<table border="1" cellpadding="1" cellspacing="1" class="w-100">\n\t<tbody>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style="background-color:#f5f2f0">\n\t\t\t<pre>\n<span style="font-family:Verdana,Geneva,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:10pt"><span style="background-color:white"><strong><span style="color:navy">package </span></strong><span style="color:black">com.laptrinhjavaweb.api;\n\n</span><strong><span style="color:navy">import </span></strong><span style="color:black">org.springframework.boot.SpringApplication;\n\n</span><strong><span style="color:navy">import </span></strong><span style="color:black">org.springframework.boot.autoconfigure.</span><span style="color:olive">SpringBootApplication</span><span style="color:black">;\n\n</span><span style="color:olive">@SpringBootApplication\n\n</span><strong><span style="color:navy">public class </span></strong><span style="color:black">Application {\n&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><strong><span style="color:navy">public static void </span></strong><span style="color:black">main(String[] args) {\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; SpringApplication.<em>run</em>(Application.</span><strong><span style="color:navy">class</span></strong><span style="color:black">, args);\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; }\n}</span></span></span></span></pre>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span style="font-family:Verdana,Geneva,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:14px">9.&nbsp;Tiếp tục l&agrave;m theo h&igrave;nh b&ecirc;n dưới</span></span></p>\n\n<p style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family:Verdana,Geneva,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:14px"><img alt="" src="https://laptrinhjavaweb.com/repository/ckfinder/images/tao-project-spring-boot-6.png" style="height:500px" /></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style="font-family:Verdana,Geneva,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:14px">Trong folder src/main/resources tạo file application.properties v&agrave; add đoạn code b&ecirc;n dưới v&agrave;o file</span></span></p>\n\n<table border="1" cellpadding="1" cellspacing="1" class="w-100">\n\t<tbody>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style="background-color:#f5f2f0">\n\t\t\t<pre>\n<span style="font-family:Verdana,Geneva,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:10pt"><span style="background-color:white"><strong><span style="color:navy">server.port</span></strong><span style="color:black">=</span><strong><span style="color:blue">8081</span></strong></span></span></span></pre>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p><span style="font-family:Verdana,Geneva,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:14px">10. Sau khi ho&agrave;n th&agrave;nh c&aacute;c bưới kể tr&ecirc;n, run project:</span></span></p>\n\n<p style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family:Verdana,Geneva,sans-serif"><img alt="" src="https://laptrinhjavaweb.com/repository/ckfinder/images/tao-project-spring-boot-7.png" style="height:500px" /></span></p>\n\n<p><span style="font-family:Verdana,Geneva,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:14px">Kết quả th&agrave;nh c&ocirc;ng khi bạn mở tr&igrave;nh duyệt v&agrave; truy cập v&agrave;o link:</span></span></p>\n\n<p style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family:Verdana,Geneva,sans-serif"><img alt="" src="https://laptrinhjavaweb.com/repository/ckfinder/images/tao-project-spring-boot-8.png" style="width:500px" /></span></p>\n\n<p style="text-align:center">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<div id="tao-project-spring-boot-java-web-1-5-X">&nbsp;</div>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span style="font-family:Verdana,Geneva,sans-serif"><span style="color:#e74c3c"><strong><span style="font-size:16px">2. Tạo project spring boot ph&aacute;t triển web</span></strong></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style="font-family:Verdana,Geneva,sans-serif">[Đang update]</span></p>\n\n<h2><span style="font-family:Verdana,Geneva,sans-serif"><strong>Kh&oacute;a học s